Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8), autotools-dev, libtool, dh-autoreconf
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/ucimf
Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/pkg-ime/openvanilla-modules.git
