Package: openvanilla-imgeneric
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: generic library of openvanilla input method
 OpenVanilla is a collection of popular CJK and symbol input methods 
 and language tools. 
 .
 This package contains openvanilla's generic library files.

